dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Initiating Voice Log.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: This is Control Team Captain Agent Faust. Logging today's Work records.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: My current location is... the Lobotomy Corporation Headquarters. Upper Layer, Control Team Department.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: It has been 9 days since the Manager's first day at work. 3 days have passed since the Information Team Department opened.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: The Clerks are almost all here... It is quite busy.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: This voice log will resume when Management Work begins. Pausing the recording.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: ... Resuming Voice Log.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: I am... currently headed to educate our new hires.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Also, the Manager has requested that I be assigned to manage the new Abnormality we received yesterday. It appears that the personnel newly deployed to the Control Team has expired.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: It seems that we've hired a new employee...

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Oh, Excuse me... (Shuffling noises)

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Hello, Jacob. What is it? You are hesitating outside the containment unit.

dataList.title: Level 1 Agent
dataList.content: Ah, Team Captain Faust... I-It's my first assignment, and I'm... a bit scared....

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: There is no cause for concern, Jacob. The Abnormality assigned to you is likely to be the safest Abnormality here.

dataList.title: Level 1 Agent
dataList.content: But... Its name here, look... It's really intimidating...

dataList.title: Level 1 Agent
dataList.content: One Sin and Hundreds of Good Deeds...

dataList.title: Level 1 Agent
dataList.content: Team Captain! W-what happens if I get unlucky and the thing decides to commit that one Sin against me? I-I don't... I still haven't...

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Relax. That is not how this Abnormality behaves.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Peruse the Abnormality Details, and conduct Insight or Attachment Works. And nothing will happen.

dataList.title: Level 1 Agent
dataList.content: R-really...?

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Faust does not lie.

dataList.title: Level 1 Agent
dataList.content: O-okay. Thank you, Team Captain.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: ... We are running somewhat behind schedule. Jacob is one of the newest hires assigned to the Control Team. It appears he was unnecessarily intimidated by a brief description of the Abnormality.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: I suppose this is a part of a Team Captain's job. I am certain that the Manager will be understanding.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Then... I will continue this recording once I arrive at the containment unit.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Testing, testing. Resuming Voice Log.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: My arrival was delayed beyond my initial predictions... I had a run-in with Ms. Malkuth, and had the pleasure of exchanging a few words with her.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: She inquired about the Work we had planned for the day, so I made an impromptu report.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: While it was unexpected that she wanted to know the expected completion time down to the seconds, I believe that records were helpful in giving her a satisfactory answer.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: She is a Sephirah, after all. She is responsible for an entire department. Her demands are not entirely unreasonable.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Moving on... This is the containment unit of T-01-54, also known as the Forsaken Murderer.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: According to the prior records... As long as the Work results are good, there shouldn't be any difficulties with managing this Abnormality.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Hm... (Sounds of flipping through papers) Work records show that the employee previously assigned to this Abnormality conducted Repression Works.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: ... Which resulted in the overproduction of NE-Box. The Abnormality's head transformed into something akin to a metallic substance, which it used to crush the employee to death... Hm.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Not many would understand the process by which a person's head transforms from flesh to metal. But that ineffability is simply the nature of Abnormalities.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: This record at least informed me that avoiding Repression Work on this Abnormality would be preferable.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Even if something were to happen... I have an E.G.O Suit resistant against RED damage, so I foresee little trouble ahead.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: I will continue this documentation once the Work is complete.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: ... This is Faust.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: The Work was successful.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: The Abnormality was observed muttering something to itself. It shuddered with anxiety and refused to look away from the floor. A proper communication was deemed difficult.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: It looked rather emaciated, so I attempted to perform an Instinct Work by providing it food items that humans find useful.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: The results are encouraging. I will record that Instinct Work is effective for this Abnormality.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: But... I have not observed any signs of its head turning into metal, nor am I any closer to learning the mechanics behind that phenomenon.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Considering this E.G.O weapon was extracted from the Abnormality in question, it seems evident that the Abnormality's characteristics are at least partially carried over to the shape and particularities of the E.G.O weapon.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Ah, the siren...

dataList.title: Lobotomy Corporation
dataList.content: [WARNING. ORDEAL OF GREEN DAWN ALERT. SUPPRESSION PERSONNEL FROM ALL DEPARTMENTS MUST IMMEDIATELY ASSEMBLE AT THE BOTTOM RIGHT ELEVATOR OF THE UPPER LAYER.]

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: The Manager's orders have arrived via the devices. ... It is time for the Ordeals already, then.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Each employee is equipped with a device that displays orders from the Manager in text form. The devices must be checked often as the orders are rather frequent.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: I must go and assist them in Suppressing this Ordeal.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: I am not particularly concerned. Maybe this Ordeal will be Suppressed before Faust even gets there.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: The Manager does not yet know... but the Ordeal of Green Dawn is quite insignificant compared to what is to come.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: ... Hm, no. I must hold my tongue, lest I risk confusing any other individual who will be listening to this recording.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Faust is... determined to struggle, to survive the remaining 41 days of Work.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: And I will leave it at that.

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Well, then...

dataList.title: Control Team Captain
dataList.content: Faust, ending the Voice Log.
